Create Application:

JBNLayout.Application(node, {
    x: number,
    y: number,
    width: number,
    height: number,
    draggable: boolean,
    resizable: boolean,
    resizeProportionally: boolean,
    snapSize: boolean,
    snapPosition: boolean,
    droppable: boolean
});

Application methods:

JBNLayout.Application.withSelected
JBNLayout.Application.withEach

Add View:

JBNLayout.Application.add({
    x: number,
    y: number,
    width: number,
    height: number,
    editable: boolean,
    draggable: boolean,
    resizable: boolean,
    resizeProportionally: boolean,
    snapSize: boolean,
    snapPosition: boolean
});

View methods:

JBNLayout.View.update
JBNLayout.View.remove
JBNLayout.View.select
JBNLayout.View.deselect
JBNLayout.View.toHTML
JBNLayout.View.toJSON

Add Shortcuts:

JBNLayout.Application.shortcuts.add(combination, action);

Usage:

new JBNLayout.Application(node, {
	width: 400,
	height: 300
});

layout.view.add({
	width: 100,
	height: 100,
	x: 50,
	y: 50,
	editable: true,
	draggable: true,
	resizable: true
});

layout.view.toHTML();

Result:

<div class="view" style="left: 0px; top: 0px; width: 400px; height: 300px">
    <div class="view" style="left: 50px; top: 50px; width: 100px; height: 100px"></div>
</div>

Example:

http://www.dotcanvas.org/